Hi Nirmal,

Thanks for your patience, I wanted to run this requirement past Heath before we came up with the best approach. We have looked into coding the course page on the northernsydneysurgery.org.au website for you. I’m afraid it won’t be as quick and easy a process as I had hoped. We would need to do extensive work on the site, which is best left to NSS’s team or developer contacts. It’s far easier and safer when the sites are in our controlled environments. I’m sure they should be able to accommodate this need for you. If we can help in any other way, please do let us know.
